==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Transmigration
<hw>Trans`mi*gra"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>transmigration</ets>, L. <ets>transmigratio</ets>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of passing from one country to another;
migration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The passing of the soul at death into another mortal
body; metempsychosis.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Transmigrator</ent>⟦br⟧
